  ---
  Most common workflow

  Got a new stock file?
  1. Put the new .xls file in All the Files with material here/
  2. Update the filename in scripts/import-stock.ts (line xlsPath)
  3. Run npm run db:import-stock

  Changed something in the UI?
  1. npm run dev — test locally
  2. npm run build — make sure it compiles
  3. git add ... && git commit -m "..." — save